**タイトル:** SCP-6051 - 冬将軍
**原著者:** [[*user thesilentking]]
**作成年:** 2021
**訳者:** [[*user Sito-Kyu]]
**日本語版作成年:** 2024
[[include :scp-jp:credit:end]]

[[module css]]

[[include :scp-jp:component:anomaly-class-bar-source

|item-number= 6051
|clearance= 3
|container-class= esoteric
|secondary-class= cernunnos
|secondary-icon= https://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Aanomaly-class-bar/cernunnos-icon.svg
|disruption-class= ekhi
|risk-class= danger
